title: [Daniele Teti]Delphi Cookbook(pdf){Zzzzz}
description:
Delphi XE5 Cookbook is intended for those who are wellversed with the basics of RAD Studio, or for seasoned users who are migrating from the earlier versions of RAD. Even for nonseasoned RAD Studio programmers, there are an abundance of references available to get you up to speed before beginning to read this book. Along with the background knowledge in app development, it is also assumed that you are proficient in C++.

Publisher: Packt Publishing (27 September 2014)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1783559586
ISBN-13: 978-1783559589
